593
00:29:29,970 --> 00:29:31,800
I don't know what happened.

594
00:29:40,700 --> 00:29:41,830
Dad.

595
00:29:41,830 --> 00:29:43,130
Dad.

596
00:29:43,130 --> 00:29:44,900
Wasn't Weikang just having a cold?

597
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:47,530
