610
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:11,060
I'll notify the colleagues there first.

611
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:13,670
Dad.

612
00:30:15,100 --> 00:30:16,070
Go home and rest first.

613
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,030
Don't stay here.

614
00:30:17,030 --> 00:30:19,230
I'll ask Sister Peng to take care of him.

615
00:30:19,870 --> 00:30:21,370
Every word you just said,

616
00:30:21,370 --> 00:30:23,600
