619
00:30:36,830 --> 00:30:38,900
Haven't you thought about that?

620
00:31:57,700 --> 00:31:58,830
Thank you.

621
00:31:58,830 --> 00:32:01,470
Deng Weiyu, why are you here?

622
00:32:02,170 --> 00:32:03,630
Mom,

623
00:32:03,630 --> 00:32:04,470
