don't let him get involved anymore.

859
00:42:39,700 --> 00:42:40,870
Why?

860
00:42:40,870 --> 00:42:43,130
That Jiang Zhihao

861
00:42:43,130 --> 00:42:45,530
is just like his mother, networking everywhere.

862
00:42:45,530 --> 00:42:48,030
Who knows what he's plotting behind our backs.

863
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:50,600
Aunt Xiurong isn't that kind of person, is she?

864
00:42:50,600 --> 00:42:51,700
I'm talking about

865
00:42:51,700 --> 00:42:53,800
his biological mother.

866
00:43:01,530 --> 00:43:03,830
How do you know about this?

867
00:43:07,200 --> 00:43:08,570
If it weren't for Yongkuan

868
00:43:08,570 --> 00:43:10,430
driving away that annoying woman,

869
00:43:10,430 --> 00:43:11,830
you and I

870
00:43:11,830 --> 00:43:14,960
probably wouldn't have even set foot in the Deng family.

871
00:43:19,970 --> 00:43:21,900
Zhihao is quite pitiful,

872
00:43:21,900 --> 00:43:24,070
an unwanted illegitimate child.

873
00:43:24,900 --> 00:43:27,430
He still doesn't know anything.

874
00:43:30,130 --> 00:43:31,800
What do you mean?

875
00:43:32,970 --> 00:43:34,570
It means

876
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:39,200
We finally got rid of Deng Weikang.

877
00:43:40,830 --> 00:43:43,960
You're not thinking of going after another one, are you?

878
00:45:32,130 --> 00:45:34,600
If one day Linlin lets you take the lead,

879
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:35,700
what would you do?

880
00:45:35,700 --> 00:45:36,600
Who is that woman?

881
00:45:36,600 --> 00:45:37,800
That's Deng Weijie.

882
00:45:38,430 --> 00:45:39,430
Deng Weijie.

883
00:45:39,430 --> 00:45:41,570
Haven't I suffered enough these past few years?

884
00:45:41,570 --> 00:45:43,530
You will never become He Meixia.

885
00:45:44,200 --> 00:45:46,570
I just happened to remember someone.

886
00:45:46,570 --> 00:45:48,700
Tell me who that bastard is.

887
00:45:48,700 --> 00:45:49,870
He Meixia.

888
00:45:49,870 --> 00:45:51,930
Do you even consider me a friend?

889
00:45:51,930 --> 00:45:53,430
No matter what happens,

890
00:45:53,430 --> 00:45:55,230
I'll always be by your side.

891
00:45:56,230 --> 00:45:57,200
I just want an answer.

892
00:45:57,200 --> 00:45:59,530
This is called making a fuss over nothing.

893
00:45:59,900 --> 00:46:01,900
Deng Weiyu, what are you looking at?

894
00:46:02,670 --> 00:46:03,570
Looking at you.
